November 28, 1973; 50 years ago today, 5 Top American 🇺🇸 designers @annekleinofficial @billblassusa @halston @oscardelarenta @stephenburrowsworld went to Paris with @officiallizaminnelli for a fashion competition against 5 Top French 🇫🇷 designers @dior @emanuelungaroparis @givenchy @pierrecardin @ysl to raise funds for the crumbling Palace of Versailles. The event now famously known as “The Battle of Versailles” put American fashion, American designers and a new generation of influential fashion models, many of color on the world stage changing fashion forever.
